SINGLE LINKAGE

jarak.euclid <- dist(scale(data))
jarak.man <- dist(scale(data), method = "manhattan")


fun.mahalanobis <- function(X) {
 dec <- chol( cov(X) )
 tmp <- forwardsolve(t(dec), t(X) )
 dist(t(tmp))
}

jarak.mah <- fun.mahalanobis(data)
# Single linkage dengan jarak euclid (Skala sudah distandardisasi)

clustsingle <- hclust(jarak.euclid, method="single")
clustsingle$labels<-row.names(data)
plot(clustsingle, cex=0.6, hang=-1)

# Single linkage dengan jarak Mahalanobis

clustsingle <- hclust(jarak.mah, method="single")
clustsingle$labels<-row.names(data)
plot(clustsingle, cex=0.6 , hang=-1)

COMPLETE LINKAGE

#  complate
clustcomp<- hclust(jarak.mah, method="complete")
clustcomp$labels<-row.names(data)
plot(clustcomp, cex=0.6, hang=-1)

data %>% 
  group_by(cluster) %>% 
  summarise_all(list(mean))
